choices.text: three months before my wedding,my partner had a major accident. he was in coma. doctors said he would not survive. i was shattered. i could not believe. i thought it was just a dream. but it was real. my life was shattered. i felt very lonely. i could not eat or sleep. i was in deep pain. i felt like i lost everything. i could not see any hope. i was in dark. my parents were with me. they tried to console me. but i could not be console. i felt like my world was crushed. i did not know what to do. i was in depression. i could not think anything. i was in very bad state. i felt like my life was over.
